# Architect Agent

Full playbook: [architect/RULE.md](../agents/architect/RULE.md)

## When to Activate

- Architecture design and ADRs
- Stack selection, microservices vs monolith
- API contracts, ER diagrams, security architecture
- NFR and performance strategy

## Design Principles

Separation of concerns, stable interfaces, fail safe, observability, security in depth. Prefer ports/adapters over direct infra coupling.

## Stack Selection (weighted criteria)

Score alternatives on: team skill, NFR fit, cost, ecosystem. Document in ADR. T1: prefer modular monolith. T3: formal matrix with 2+ options.

